widgets.label: OSC{/track/@{parent.variables.n}/volume/str}
widgets.color: JS{{var val = OSC{/track/@{parent.variables.n}/vu} if (val < 0.6) { return "lime"}{ else if (val < 0.7) {return "yellow" }{ else { return "red"}}}

widgets.css: #{ threshold = 0.5;value = @{this};animationcount = value >= threshold ? "infinite": "0";}@keyframes blink {0% {opacity:1;}50% {opacity:0.5;}}.toggle:after {animation: blink .5s steps(1) #{animationcount};}

widgets.label: auto
widgets.color: JS{{var val = @{this} if (val < 0.8) { return "red"}{ else if (val < 0.9) {return "yellow" }{ else { return "lime"}}}

widgets.css: #{ threshold = 0.5;value = @{this};animationcount = value >= threshold ? "infinite": "0";}@keyframes blink {0% {opacity:1;}50% {opacity:0.5;}}.toggle:after {animation: blink .5s steps(1) #{animationcount};}
